{"id": "art-283", "label": "Art. 283", "title": "Art. 283", "slug": "art-283", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:\nblack'>Art. 283 </span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1223467335\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1037\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1223467335\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<span class=SpellE>Societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>,\norganizate în baza <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legii</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>15/1990</span><span style='color:black'> privind\nreorganizarea <span class=SpellE>unit&#259;&#355;ilor</span> economice de stat\nca regii autonome <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;i</span>,\ncu modific&#259;rile ulterioare, privatizate sau care se vor privatiza, pot <span\nclass=SpellE>func&#355;iona</span> numai pe baz&#259; de statut.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_8392496\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1036\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_8392496\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)Modificând, în <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iile</span>\n<i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>, statutul, <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span>\nîl pot denumi act constitutiv, f&#259;r&#259; ca prin aceasta s&#259; ia <span\nclass=SpellE>na&#351;tere</span> o societate nou&#259;.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='color:black'>(3)La <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nexistente, <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ii</span> pot modifica actul\nconstitutiv, prev&#259;zând în el documentele la care <span class=SpellE>ace&#351;tia</span>\nurmeaz&#259; s&#259; aib&#259; acces, în sensul art. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>8 lit. i)</span><span style='color:black'>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1477974235\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1035\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1477974235\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)<span class=SpellE>Societ&#259;&#355;ile</span> cu\ncapital integral ori majoritar de stat pot <span class=SpellE>func&#355;iona</span>\ncu orice num&#259;r de <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span>.</span><br\nstyle='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![if !supportLineBreakNewLine]><br style='mso-special-character:line-break'>\n<![endif]></p>"}